metadata.name: DON'T'LAG 2 [outtake]
metadata.description:
DON'T'LAG 2 [outtake] is the official and exclusive outtake of the following artwork combining music, dance, and architecture:

https://milianmori.com/projects/don-t-lag-2

Your purchase of this piece supports future episodes of this series. 

Abstract:
DON'T'LAG suggests a club culture where identities are effortlessly dancing to rhythms beyond 4/4 grooves. The trinity of movement, architecture and music are synchronised, delivering a feel of an uncompromising, raw but sensual domain. 

Credits:
Music and Concept: Milian Mori
Dance and Choreography: Élie Autin
Cinematography: Emanuel Demenga, 
Maximilian Hochstrasser
Producer: Milian Mori
Graphics: Sandi Gazić
Architecture: Kunsthaus Bregenz, Peter Zumthor
